#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:271
msgid "``env``"
msgstr ""

# 6e706c8757a246b7a5e93439dcbd172b
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:270
msgid ""
"A dictionary object containing the environment of the documentation "
"processor in its state at the time of the reference encounter."
msgstr ""

# f6c6b4ff17d04cc5bd3e70d1b156abf6
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:274
msgid "``ref_node``"
msgstr ""

# db8df53809be405b9d0d279c7560cad2
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:274
msgid ""
"The node object of the reference as encountered in the documentation "
"source."
msgstr ""

# 1ff34243b76d40b09bc476fbf6c2f402
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:278
msgid "``explicit_title_p``"
msgstr ""

# 49e92b6dd5954fe99f2f86d98b6b966f
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:277
msgid ""
"Contains the text content of the reference's explicit title overriding, "
"if present in the reference markup."
msgstr ""

# 7c998a59aed242359b0b6b46f0231df9
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:283
msgid "``title``"
msgstr ""

# 1782a39d3f6d4819bd406d975a1de9ae
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:281
msgid ""
"The processed form of the reference title, which may be the result of "
"domain class transformations or an overriding of the reference title "
"within the reference itself."
msgstr ""

# ac5e13c05b944da185d7d4678319d411
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:288
msgid "``target``"
msgstr ""

# 48a4e4ff2db54b5488bc2fd9c3fffbff
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:286
msgid ""
"The computed target of the reference, suitable for use by Sphinx to "
"construct hyperlinks to the location of the item's definition, wherever "
"it may reside in the final rendered form of the documentation."
msgstr ""

# ce47005dc04441ea9d74b9338c70632a
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:290
msgid ""
"In our reference class, we have simply returned the processed title "
"(allowing the documentation to override the variable's name if desired, "
"or defaulting to the domain class's representation of the variable name "
"in all other cases) and the parser's computed target."
msgstr ""

# 670e0ba0452a460bb09ee48c1bfd63a9
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/adding-domains.en.rst:295
msgid ""
"It is recommended to leave the ``target`` untouched, however you may "
"choose to perform any transformations you wish on the value of the "
"``title``, bearing in mind that whatever string is returned will appear "
"verbatim in the rendered documentation everywhere references for this "
"domain are used."
msgstr ""

# f493a9908ace42d8a1e2c729913c1a05
